message.content: cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.MED, cs.AI, cs.NEURON - The paper deals with the application of deep learning techniques for the segmentation of pathological shoulder muscles from MRI images. This falls under the domain of computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper focuses on medical imaging (cs.MED) and proposes novel architectures for improving segmentation accuracy (cs.AI). The use of pre-trained encoders also suggests the involvement of neural networks (cs.NEURON).
